---
title: Sirloin Steak and Truffled Mushroom Sauce with Roast Potatoes
description: This Sirloin Steak and Truffled Mushroom Sauce is a luxurious dinner night option, made with premium ingredients for a real taste of luxury at home!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sirloin-steak-and-truffled-mushroom-sauce-875337ec-4b19f9cd.jpg
